@Shitnotworking: Yes.
Currently there are not many posts(other than 'Hello ZeroMe!') on PedoHub(not much activity). Many make an account and are either lurking here or notice there's not much content and leave.
But that's for PedoHub specifically, ZeroMe as a whole has quite a lot of posts and is fairly active. If you want to see what the rest of ZeroMe is doing I suggest you download most or all of the hubs for ZeroMe. As far as I know there are [Innocentchilds room](/1J1epG5eMc4bsmh69UctBg4PHEe5B3kYHY/hubs.html) and [GetAllHub](/1GLndW2MJn7japuF3X2tbfBqgPMR52zaLQ)(outdated) that maintain a list of ZeroMe hubs.

@Cp-lurker: So, a degree in advertising, I take it?
>my GF broke up with me after 5 years.
Sucks to hear that.

@Rinoa: You already do. PedoHub is (at the moment) only an ZeroMe hub that stores the content provided by it's users. Hubs(technically they are called `mergers`) on ZeroNet are designed to be a federated system and PedoHub is no exception. Think mastodon/gnusocial or matrix only without central servers at all.
>but i can't see the hub, only the first hub. 

I'm not sure what you mean.

@Rinoa: Out if interest: Have you red the info on PedoHub?
Many people seem to be confused about 'access to the Hub' or 'where the content on this Hub is', so either most don't read the text(or just skim over it, I can't blame them it's quite a lot) or have red the text but didn't understand it/got the wrong idea, because it was unclear/too technical to understand.
Just wanna figure out which is the case.

@Securitycypher: Have you clicked on the `Everyone` section?
If you see a bunch of `Hello ZeroMe!` messages then you already should be able to see what's there.
Please note that ZeroMe is a micro blogging platform and since the user activity on PedoHub is really low, there isn't really much content to see(at the current point in time anyways).

@Littlemermaid: No this is basically just something to micro blog on(think twitter), but (at least on pedohub) posting childporn and talking about pedo topics and so on are completely allowed.

For childporn you can take a look at my ZeroMe profile bio, I have listed a couple imageboard-boards that have cp or other ontopic content on them.
If you have any more questions feel free to ask at any time, while I'm not always around I try to answer you as soon as I can.
